1
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,570
Brother Bai,

2
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:07,920
I think it's time to plan my return to the palace.

3
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,520
After all, the longer I stay in the Bai Manor,

4
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:11,480
the more danger I might bring to you.

5
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,120
Alright.

6
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:15,840
Third Prince, what a coincidence.

7
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,920
How is it a coincidence again?

8
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:21,360
It really is a wonderful fate.

9
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,740
Sister, what happened to you?

10
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,170
Did someone beat you up?

11
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,240
Well, Brother Bai,

12
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,200
why don't you two talk?

13
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,300
I'll take my leave.

14
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,900
It's quite unique.

15
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,360
Am I too dazzling today?

16
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,759
He likes people who are low-key.

17
00:01:57,759 --> 00:02:00,040
Sister, I don't mean to lecture you,

18
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,970
but there's something wrong with your taste.

19
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,520
It looks good.

20
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:18,640
Sister-in-law, what do you usually like to do?

21
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,240
Practice with the spear and read.

22
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,960
Why do you do those things?

23
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,160
Practicing with the spear calms the mind.

24
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,490
Reading brings wisdom.

25
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:28,920
Both are essential for leading an army.

26
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:32,160
What kind of books do you like to read?

27
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,640
Books on strategy and history,

28
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:34,960
laws and people's livelihood,

29
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,240
and medicine.

30
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:37,760
As long as they're useful,

31
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,090
I can never read enough.

32
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,360
You truly are a general's daughter.

33
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,290
It's a pity you married my brother.

34
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,000
Chaohua,

35
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,880
why do you ask?

36
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,560
Nothing.

37
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,600
I just wanted to get to know you better.

38
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,320
I'll let you get back to it.

39
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,250
I'm leaving now.

40
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,680
Adai.

41
00:02:59,200 --> 00:02:59,840
Come on.

42
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,920
Horse stance.

43
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,800
Straighten your shoulders.

44
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,840
Hold the spear.

45
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,520
Thrust like a dragon!

46
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:21,920
Go!

47
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,880
That's ridiculous.

48
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,840
Stupid spear.

49
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,000
Again.

50
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,170
Try another one.

51
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:52,040
Why does it look so easy when she does it?

52
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,640
So annoying.

53
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,180
Why are you copying me?

54
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,770
Sister-in-law.

55
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,240
I just admire you.

56
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,330
I want to be as strong as you.

57
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,280
Then let me teach you.

58
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,200
Hold this.

59
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,810
Turn this hand over.

60
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,800
Hold it tight. Raise this side.

61
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,180
Get into the horse stance.

62
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,160
Good.

63
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,570
Try it yourself.

64
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,880
You're amazing.

65
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:57,960
Bone of Wind.

66
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,520
Eye of Fire.

67
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,680
Please show me the way.

68
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,880
It's her scent.

69
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:15,060
To awaken the Wolf King's bloodline within her,

70
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:19,240
we must destroy her reason,

71
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,220
and make her lose control.

72
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:24,600
Let everything return to the wild.

73
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,410
Once I enter the palace,

74
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,000
I can be with the Third Prince every day.

75
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,330
Who said you could sit here?

76
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,880
This is the Prime Minister's Manor.

77
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,280
I'll sit wherever I want.

78
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:46,280
Sister, you don't know yet, do you?

79
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,560
Word has already spread on the street.

80
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,040
I am the true chosen one.

81
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,980
News has come from the Palace.

82
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:55,120
It's set in stone that I'll be entering the Palace.

83
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,800
Entering the Palace?

84
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,240
To marry whom?

85
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,280
The Third Prince, of course.

86
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:02,680
What are you laughing at?

87
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,880
I'm laughing at your good fortune, Sister.

88
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:05,800
Of course.

89
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,780
My mother was of nobler birth than yours.

90
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:11,200
Naturally, I'll marry better than you too.

91
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,920
Shen Lingbo, seeing me in my glory now,

92
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,600
you're burning with jealousy, aren't you?

93
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,800
Go kill that little slut...

94
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:23,080
...and that little bastard for me.

95
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,540
Your mother...

96
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:29,600
If that playboy Bai Manchuan hadn't taken pity on you...

97
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,040
and plotted against my father,

98
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,120
you wouldn't even have set foot in the Prime Minister's manor.

99
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,520
You'd better shut up now.

100
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:37,520
Did I hit a nerve again?

101
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:44,320
You went to the Hundred Flowers Pavilion every day for Bai Manchuan.

102
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:47,580
Who knew that loser Bai Manchuan still wouldn't marry you?

103
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,720
It's truly pathetic to watch.

104
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,240
Say one more word,

105
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,900
and I'll send you to meet your mother.

106
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:59,520
Do you know how your mother died?

107
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,130
What do you mean?

108
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:07,080
Your mother seemed impressive back then,

109
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:09,600
but she was actually a hollow fool.

110
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,840
That she lived as long as she did...

111
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,840
was only because I showed her mercy.

112
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:17,040
Your mother used her status as the legal wife of the Prime Minister's manor

113
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,000
to torture servants

114
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,460
and bully the concubines.

115
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:23,240
In the end, she watched helplessly as she was plotted against step by step,

116
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,370
unable to do a thing,

117
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,440
until she met a sudden death.

118
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,600
No...

119
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,400
It was you.

120
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,600
You killed my mother.

121
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,280
There were too many people who wanted your mother dead.

122
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:44,280
I just gave things a little push.

123
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:48,520
Debts must always be paid.

124
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,320
What do you want to do?

125
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:54,600
When I first entered the Prime Minister's manor, I swore...

126
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,840
I would take all the grievances I suffered...

127
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,600
and pay them back, bit by bit.

128
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,540
Don't be foolish anymore.

129
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,440
Okay?

130
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:21,800
Now it's my turn to counterattack.

131
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,060
You're not asleep?

132
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,360
This is called luring the enemy in.

133
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,400
I'm leaving.

134
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,039
Huang Huacai is murdering her husband!

135
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,700
Stop shouting!

136
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,760
This is called close-quarters combat.

137
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,800
Sister-in-law.

138
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:03,200
Sis, didn't I tell you to knock before entering?

139
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:06,320
Sister-in-law, I want to study with you.

140
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:07,160
No.

141
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,720
Your sister-in-law is my private tutor.

142
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,360
Why?

143
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,580
Sister-in-law belongs to everyone.

144
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,400
Brother, don't be so selfish.

145
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,960
Sis, that's a real awl!

146
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,920
Bai Manchuan!

147
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,800
You don't play fair!
